  Locus:
    Page: 349
    Verse: 19
Tags:
  - Past
---
Regrets are caused by a misuse of memory. ... The man who broods over the past
can never master the difficulties of today. Every wise man learns to forget.
He does not allow himself to become a slave to his memory.
